{{Infobox medical condition (new)|name=Whooping cough|risks=|frequency=16.3 million (2015)<!-- incidence table --><ref name=GBD2015Pre/>|medication=|treatment=[[Antibiotics]] (if started early)<ref name=CDC2013Tr/>|prevention=[[Pertussis vaccine]]<ref name=Update10/>|differential=|diagnosis=[[Nasopharyngeal swab]]<ref name=CDC2013Sam/>|causes=''[[Bordetella pertussis]]'' ([[airborne disease|spread through the air]])<ref name=CDC2014C/>|synonyms=Pertussis, 100-day cough|duration=~ 10 weeks<ref name=CDC2015Facts/>|onset=|complications=Vomiting, [[rib fracture|broken ribs]], [[fatigue (medicine)|very tired]]<ref name=CDC2014S/><ref name=CDC2013Com/>|symptoms=Runny nose, fever, cough<ref name=CDC2014S/>|field=[[Infectious disease (medical specialty)|Infectious disease]]|caption=A young boy coughing due to pertussis.|image=Pertussis.jpg|deaths=58,700 (2015)<ref name=GBD2015De/>}}{{Infobox disease|Name=Whooping cough|Image=Pertussis.jpg|Caption=A young boy coughing due to pertussis.|DiseasesDB=1523|ICD10={{ICD10|A|37||a|30}}|ICD9={{ICD9|033}}|ICDO=|OMIM=|MedlinePlus=001561|eMedicineSubj=emerg|eMedicineTopic=394|eMedicine_mult={{eMedicine2|ped|1778}}|MeshID=D014917}}<!-- Definition and symptoms -->'''Chifuwa chokoka mtima,''' chomwe chimadziwikanso kuti  '''chifuwa cha masiku 100,''' ndi matenda omwe anthu amapatsirana mosavuta ndipo chimayambitsidwa ndi [[Bacterial disease|mabakiteriya]].<ref>{{cite journal|author=Carbonetti NH|title=Immunomodulation in the pathogenesis of Bordetella pertussis infection and disease|journal=Curr Opin Pharmacol|volume=7|issue=3|pages=272–8|date=June 2007|pmid=17418639|doi=10.1016/j.coph.2006.12.004}}</ref><ref name="CDC2014S2">{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Signs & Symptoms|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/about/signs-symptoms.html|accessdate=12 February 2015|date=May 22, 2014}}</ref> Matendawa akamayamba kumene, zizindikiro zake zimakhala zofanana ndi za [[Common cold|chifuwa wamba komanso chimfine]] ndipo wodwala amatuluka mamina, [[Fever|amatentha thupi]] ndiponso [[Cough|amakhosomola]] mwa apo ndi apo.<!-- <ref name=CDC2014S/> --> Pakapita nthawi, wodwalayo amayamba kukhosomola kwambiri.<!-- <ref name=CDC2014S/> --> Ndiyeno wodwalayo amayamba kukhosomola modetsa nkhawa ndiponso amabanika.<ref name="CDC2014S2" /> Wodwalayo angakhosomole kwa masiku opitirira 100 kapena milungu 10.<ref>{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Fast Facts|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/fast-facts.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=12 February 2015|date=February 13, 2014}}</ref> Wodwalayo angakhosomole kwambiri  mpaka kufika posanza, [[Rib fracture|kuvulala m'nthiti]], kapena kufika [[Fatigue (medicine)|potopa kwambiri]] mpaka kumalephera kukhosomala bwinobwino.<ref name="CDC2014S2" /><ref name="CDC2013Com2">{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Complications|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/about/complications.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=12 February 2015|date=August 28, 2013}}</ref> Ana omwe sanakwanitse chaka chimodzi kawirikawiri sakhosomola kwenikweni koma m'malo mwake [[Apnea|amangobanika kwa kanthawi ndithu]].<ref name="CDC2014S2" /> Nthawi zambiri pamadutsa masiku oyambira pa 7 mpaka 10 kuchokera pa nthawi imene tizilombo toyambitsa matendawa talowa m'thupi la munthu kuti munthuyo ayambe kusonyeza zizindikiro.<ref name="CDC2012Pink2">{{cite book|last1=Atkinson|first1=William|title=Pertussis Epidemiology and Prevention of Vaccine-Preventable Diseases|date=May 2012|publisher=Public Health Foundation|isbn=9780983263135|pages=215–230|edition=12|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/pubs/pinkbook/pert.html}}</ref> Nthawi zina anthu amene anapatsidwa katemera wa matendawa amatha kudwala koma matendawa sakhala a mphamvu kwambiri.<ref name="CDC2014S2" /><!-- Cause and diagnosis -->Matenda a chifuwa chokoka mtima amayambitsidwa ndi mabakiteriya otchedwa ''[[Bordetella pertussis]]''.<!-- <ref name=CDC2014C/> --> Anthu amapatsirana matendawa [[Airborne disease|kudzera mu mpweya]] ndipo amafalikira mosavuta munthu yemwe ali ndi tizilombo toyambitsa matendawa wakhosomula kapena kuyetsemula.<ref name="CDC2014C">{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Causes & Transmission|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/about/causes-transmission.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=12 February 2015|date=September 4, 2014}}</ref> Wodwala akhoza kupatsira ena matendawa kungoyambira pamene wayamba kusonyeza zizindikiro mpaka kufika pa milungu itatu atayamba kukhosomola modetsa nkhawa.<!-- <ref name=CDC2013Tr/> --> Odwala amene alandira mankhwala [[Antibiotic|olimbana ndi mabakiteriya]] sangapatsire ena matendawa ngati papita masiku 4 kuchokera pamene anayamba kumwa mankhwalawa.<ref name="CDC2013Tr">{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Treatment|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/clinical/treatment.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=13 February 2015|date=August 28, 2013}}</ref> Madokotala amafunika [[Nasopharyngeal swab|kuyeza makhololo kapena mamina]] kuti adziwe ngati munthu ali ndi matendawa.<!-- <ref name=CDC2013Sam/> --> Ndiyenso madokotala angayeze zinthu zimenezi pogwiritsa ntchito njira zosiyanasiyana monga yotchedwa [[culture]] kapena yotchedwa [[polymerase chain reaction]].<ref name="CDC2013Sam">{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Specimen Collection|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/clinical/diagnostic-testing/specimen-collection.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=13 February 2015|date=August 28, 2013}}</ref><!-- Prevention and treatment -->Matendawa angapewedwe ndi [[Vaccination|katemera]] monga [[Pertussis vaccine|katemera wa chifuwa chokoka mtima]].<ref name="Update10">{{cite journal|author=Heininger U|title=Update on pertussis in children|journal=Expert review of anti-infective therapy|volume=8|issue=2|pages=163–73|date=February 2010|pmid=20109046|doi=10.1586/eri.09.124}}</ref> Azaumoyo amalimbikitsa makolo kuti ana onse a milungu 6 mpaka 8 ayenera kupatsidwa katemera woyambirira yemwe amakhala wa magawo anawo.<ref>{{cite journal|title=Revised guidance on the choice of pertussis vaccines: July 2014.|journal=Wkly Epidemiol Rec|date=Jul 2014|volume=89|issue=30|pages=337–40|pmid=25072068|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2013/wer8930.pdf?ua=1}}</ref> Koma mphamvu za katemerayu zimachepa pakapita zaka zingapo ndipo azaumoyo amalimbikitsa kuti ana akulirapo komanso akuluakulu azipatsidwanso katemerayu.<ref>{{cite journal|title=Pertussis vaccines: WHO position paper.|journal=Wkly Epidemiol Rec.|date=Oct 1, 2010|volume=85|issue=40|pages=385–400|pmid=20939150}}</ref> Anthu amene akhala pafupi ndi munthu yemwe akudwala matendawa angamwe mankhwala olimbana ndi mabakiteriya pofuna kudziteteza kuti asadwale.<ref>{{cite web|title=Pertussis (Whooping Cough) Prevention|url=http://www.cdc.gov/pertussis/clinical/prevention.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=13 February 2015|date=October 10, 2014}}</ref> Koma kwa anthu amene ayamba kale kudwala matendawa, kumwa mankhwala olimbana ndi mabakiteriya patapita milungu itatu kuyambira pamene anayamba kusonyeza zizindikiro za matendawa sikuthandiza kwenikweni.<!-- <ref name=CDC2013Tr/> --> Ana osakwanitsa chaka chimodzi komanso amayi apakati angathe kumwa mankhwala olimbana ndi mabakiteriya ngati papita milungu 6 kuyambira pamene zizindikiro za matendawa zinayamba kuonekera.<!-- <ref name=CDC2013Tr/> --> Mankhwala olimbana ndi mabakiteriya omwe angagwiritsidwe ntchito ndi monga [[erythromycin]], [[azithromycin]], kapena[[trimethoprim/sulfamethoxazole]].<ref name="CDC2013Tr" /> Koma kafukufuku akusonyeza kuti mankhwala sathandiza kwenikweni pa vuto la kukhosomola kwambiri.<ref name="Wang2014">{{cite journal|last1=Wang|first6=CJ|pmid=25243777|pages=CD003257|volume=9|date=22 September 2014|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|title=Symptomatic treatment of the cough in whooping cough.|first7=A|last7=Harnden|last6=Heneghan|first1=K|first5=R|last5=Perera|first4=NW|last4=Roberts|first3=MJ|last3=Thompson|first2=S|last2=Bettiol|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD003257.pub5}}</ref> Ana ambiri osakwanitsa chaka chimodzi amagonekedwa m'chipatala chifukwa cha matendawa.<ref name="CDC2014S2" /><!-- Epidemiology and history -->Zikuoneka kuti matenda a chifuwa chokoka mtima amakhudza anthu 16&nbsp;miliyoni chaka chilichonse padziko lonse.<ref name="Wang2014" /> Ambiri mwa anthu amene amakhudzidwa ndi matendawa ndi a [[Developing world|m'mayiko amene akukwera kumene]] ndipo anthu a misinkhu yonse akukhudzidwa.<ref name="Update10" /><ref name="Wang2014" /> Mu 2013 matendawa anapha anthu 61,000 ndipo chiwerengerochi n'chocheperapo tikayerekezera ndi anthu  138,000 amene anamwalira ndi matendawa mu 1990.<ref name="GBD204">{{cite journal|last1=GBD 2013 Mortality and Causes of Death|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national age-sex specific all-cause and cause-specific mortality for 240 causes of death, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013.|journal=Lancet|date=17 December 2014|pmid=25530442|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(14)61682-2|volume=385|issue=9963|pages=117–71}}</ref> Pafupifupi ana awiri pa 100 aliwonse amene amatenga matendawa amamwalira.<ref name="CDC2013Com2" /> Mbiri imasonyeza kuti matendawa anadziwika koyamba m'zaka za ma 1500.<!-- <ref name=CDC2012Pink/> --> Mabakiteriya amene amayambitsa matendawa anadziwika koyamba mu 1906.<!-- <ref name=CDC2012Pink/> --> Katemera wa matenda a chifuwa chokoka mtima anayamba kupezeka m'zaka za m'ma 1940.<ref name="CDC2012Pink2" />

